	"chive-about-title": "About CHIVE",
	"chive-about-hero-copy": "CHIVE helps you turn data into visual insights quickly, accessibly and collaboratively.",
	"chive-about-subtitle": "An open-source tool for data exploration",
	"chive-about-intro": "Analysis, data preparation and visualization. All in the browser.",
	"chive-about-description-1": "CHIVE was born as a research project at the Federal Rural University of the Amazon (UFRA), from a real need: to simplify the exploratory data analysis process for those without familiarity with programming or complex tools.",
	"chive-about-description-2": "With CHIVE, it's possible to upload a dataset, perform data cleaning and preprocessing, and generate interactive visualizations in just a few clicks. Results can be exported as SVG, ready for use in publications, reports, and academic presentations.",
	"chive-about-description-3": "Unlike tools that require advanced technical knowledge, CHIVE focuses on accessibility — serving researchers, students, teachers, and the general public alike.",
